name: 2022 - Back on the roots
description:
On the choices that may take you down the road today, at a crossroads or not at all
The beginning of the end, the end of the beginning will be interconnected
In love, the light that accompanies it, in the darkness that accompanies
An inch of stairs to the ocean
Spacious and unlimited
Things out of control
achievement, achievement, adversity, adversity.
Rewrite, reformulate, rerun, re-destroy. Stay rebel and burn your life
